{"tid":1826944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020「和你捐」活動","createTime":"2020-01-16T14:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T04:59:31.000Z","uid":198607,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9fca98908f14991f39d619288605ad365d5020","tid":1826944,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:06:51.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次發起活動 有咩錯漏 歡迎提點<br />\n<br />\n新年就到 你有得開開心心咁過新年 但好多手足冇呢個機會 成日有人話遊行無用 和你shop無用 好 咁捐錢 一定有用啦？<br />\n<br />\n以前新年有習慣會捐少少利是錢出去 但今次見到啲偽善組織 大家心照 將啲錢放落抗爭到仲值<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qwyhpKX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqwyhpKX.png&h=e77da800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>點解係捐十分一唔係捐全部？</ins><br />\n你捐曬緊係好 但人總係自私嘅 唔通真係個個都會捐曬全部咩 始終set門檻低啲 可以吸引多啲人做 200萬人每人捐100蚊都講緊2億<br />\n<br />\n<ins>啊叔我無得收利是咁點？</ins><br />\n咁可以派利是 就當派利是俾手足 好過派俾樓下個藍絲看更喇掛？<br />\n<br />\n<ins>我有幫手懲罰黃店喎，咪間接捐咗錢囉。</ins><br />\n多謝你幫襯黃店 但始終你俾$100食野 唔係$100落曬手足身上 幫襯黃店之餘 再捐埋錢 大家fatfat<br />\n<br />\n應該點捐？<br />\n我喺張文宣到整合咗少少 我係參考 @dreamourhk <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/mobile/folders/1v4wiBqUtAhaE_JMqMmN6OOlS9pxgw57a?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Fmobile%2Ffolders%2F1v4wiBqUtAhaE_JMqMmN6OOlS9pxgw57a%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=916041e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/mobile/folders/1v4wiBqUtAhaE_JMqMmN6OOlS9pxgw57a?usp=sharing</a> 大家可以跟住佢嘅資訊總目錄excel嚟捐<br />\n<br />\n祝大家新年快樂 光復鼠年 多多捐錢"},{"pid":"b0f1b4a61d43e284af36764ae1ac4b29baf6d179","tid":1826944,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:08:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19584d4777cec224dc0dd12eccb32cc0713c59b2","tid":1826944,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /